Timeline
A project of this scope can be broken into several phases, which would typically take around 6 to 8 weeks, depending on the complexity of the data, the number of databases, and the resources involved.

Assumptions:
The project involves 2-3 databases with a moderate number of tables/columns.
Complex AI/NLP-based column name matching is optional but included in the estimate.
Existing infrastructure can be used for most of the analysis, reducing infrastructure costs.
If you provide more details (like the number of databases, columns, and the expected complexity), I can fine-tune this estimate to better match your specific project.
